                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per hour",
                    "effect": "The effigy causes spectral tentacles to erupt from the ship's hull. These tentacles lash out in an emanation with a distance equal to the ship's length and remain active for 10 minutes. Creatures in the aura and in the same body of water as the ship take a \u20132 circumstance penalty to Athletics checks to Swim as the writhing tentacles lash out in all directions.",
                    "links": [
