                "text": "The DC to break free of the tentacles is 31. When you use the figurehead's second activation to pull an enemy ship, even if you didn't pull the ship any actual distance, you can have the tentacles try to crack open its hull. The tentacles deal 7d10 bludgeoning damage to the enemy vessel (DC 31 basic Fortitude save). Apply the ship's Hardness as normal.",
